Class PathFinder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.uc3m.gade4all.AI.Astar<PathFinder.Node>
      • com.uc3m.gade4all.AI.PathFinder

  • public class PathFinder
extends Astar<PathFinder.Node>
    Pathfinder algorithm specification. Part II of AI module. Path finder adapted to a specific kind of game.It uses Astar algorithm, but it any other pathfinder algorithm may be used too.
    Author:
    Sandra Garcia Rodriguez
